# Force text treatment for source so git renders diffs even when files
# include enough non-ASCII bytes (arrows, em-dashes, etc.) to trip the
# text/binary heuristic. Without this, files that mix code and Unicode
# get displayed as `Bin N -> M bytes` and changes are hard to review.
*.ts        text
*.tsx       text
*.js        text
*.json      text
*.md        text
*.yml       text
*.yaml      text
*.sh        text eol=lf
